name: R4_v2_0550_for_R4B
title: Cross-version VS for R4.v2.0550 for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://terminology.hl7.org/ValueSet/v2-0550|2.9 for use in FHIR R4B. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R4 to R4B.
